entry.description: "TRANCHE KEY: bPIBUscVPfkwacbe/87BIjAsGSAZWKH85BzW441WqsyUSwK/NqtfuI/DuXwfjA6gDoM+7qtkbAA72Q2sQmvykcq34s4AAAAAAAAFBA== Data file: B06-9326_OBS3_c. Shotgun proteomics on the osteocytic cell line MLO-Y4, to identify new targets of the anti-osteoporosis drugs Bisphosphonates. MLO-Y4 cells were treated with the Bisphosphonate Risedronate at the concentration 10-7M for 1h and 48h. At the end of the treatment protein extracts were prepared and analysed. The proteome at the basal, untreated condition was used as a reference to whom the proteome from stimulated cells was compared to."

additional_fields.field: Nicoletta Bivi, Paola Picotti, Lukas N. Mueller, Milena Romanello, Luigi Moro, Franco Quadrifoglio and Gianluca Tell
